{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/networkparameters\/allowivindexrecoveryover42"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"According to Bluetooth Mesh Profile 1.0.1, section 3.10.5, if the IV Index"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the mesh network increased by more than 42 since the last connection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(which can take at least 48 weeks), the Node should be re-provisioned."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, as this library can be used to provision other Nodes, it should not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be blocked from sending messages to the network only because the phone wasn’t"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connected to the network for that time. This flag can disable this check,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"effectively allowing such connection."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"allowIvIndexRecoveryOver42"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The same can be achieved by clearing the app data (uninstalling and reinstalling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the app) and importing the mesh network. With no “previous” IV Index, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"library will accept any IV Index received in the Secure Network beacon upon"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connection to the GATT Proxy Node."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"int